<A>__{on jacques underwater he's swimming near the spot where he fed the moray eel. he senses something behind him and turns around. he sees a dolphin, still and silent, floating vertically. it seems to be watching him. the surprise is such that jacques is in a panic, leaps up to the surface... on jacques in bed he bolts upright, as if suddenly awakening from a dream.}
<L>__{interior room on jacques' father dark}
<A>__{a burly man, around fifty, crosses the room in the shadows and throws open the shutters with a bang. sunlight pours in. he walks over to jacques' bed in the one room house, and runs his hand through his hair.}
